  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b8bdde4f-3718-47cf-b997-3f2087442e67\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-559dee1b-fb10-4b9c-8c66-17f99da69764\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a27c869c-516a-4c3f-a5b6-52d0388099c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여러분은 메일이나 양식을 보내실 때 고민해 보신적이 없으신가요? 네이트 메일을 보면 메일에 태그성 이미지를 삽입한다거나 견적서를 보내실 때 보기 좋은 형식으로 만들고 싶다는 고민이요. 그럴 때 지금 쓰는 블로그 글을 참고해 보세요.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-96996308-07c7-4ae5-a8eb-03ed6e74d27c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-588e0bc1-217c-4daa-b0f0-db2f0506e32c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e1baa30f-8d01-4a98-b215-ee2f865be118\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-209b5af3-4df3-4001-987f-84502cade81f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>메일 이미지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8f581db-ce9f-4ea8-a687-a435c509014c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fe1949af-15b3-4ce2-92de-f6cce73be6a2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">보통 이메일을 보내실 때 하단에 이미지를 삽입하는 경우가 많습니다. 이 이미지를 명함을 스캔해서 대부분 넣는 경우가 많습니다. 하지만 명함과는 다른 정보를 넣는 것은 어떨까요? (주)파파스컴퍼니은 다음과 같은 이미지를 넣고 이메일을 전송하려고 노력중입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-03f75aa6-0901-485c-9102-2caef8701c6a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:819px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-03f75aa6-0901-485c-9102-2caef8701c6a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTZfMTEx/MDAxNjczODQ4MDE2MDk2.DdXiS6gTBYRzVJgz-dHBnxygi_IWBS3wcZHRzoPV0Vgg.-jhyFTFr2kIK7kA5MpdR25IlZQdvJ7uGmvrrH9j4_5Ug.PNG.cookthedesign/SE-03f75aa6-0901-485c-9102-2caef8701c6a.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"819\", \"originalHeight\" : \"576\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTZfMTEx/MDAxNjczODQ4MDE2MDk2.DdXiS6gTBYRzVJgz-dHBnxygi_IWBS3wcZHRzoPV0Vgg.-jhyFTFr2kIK7kA5MpdR25IlZQdvJ7uGmvrrH9j4_5Ug.PNG.cookthedesign/SE-03f75aa6-0901-485c-9102-2caef8701c6a.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-caf909df-5749-46f2-8a7d-21b962b60566\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2cda50a3-326c-4e87-88d0-03d5bdd282c1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c77240c0-d322-4eb1-b9c7-66ff129a09c6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a3e384a5-e97d-4c3c-99dd-126d758a5213\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음 이미지는 (주)파파스컴퍼니이 메일을 보낼 때 사용디는 이미지입니다. 이 이미지는 메일에서 볼 때의 사이즈와 디자인이 중요합니다. 각 회사의 내용이나 요지에 따라 거의 대부분 명함의 앞뒷면을 이용하여 디자인 리뉴얼을 진행하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1ed71f62-1e0d-4e4a-9c84-bc8b9630807b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:547px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-1ed71f62-1e0d-4e4a-9c84-bc8b9630807b\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTZfMjQy/MDAxNjczODQ4MDQ5OTg4.HdQnKTiD0OLiQ_3EGNi7FTtXxNXiF_4ntAXKwZl7qWAg.J80TRwNcd0N-i9J5j7Z_dfwencLAkcl-Eyot4rG5D84g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"547\", \"originalHeight\" : \"202\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTZfMjQy/MDAxNjczODQ4MDQ5OTg4.HdQnKTiD0OLiQ_3EGNi7FTtXxNXiF_4ntAXKwZl7qWAg.J80TRwNcd0N-i9J5j7Z_dfwencLAkcl-Eyot4rG5D84g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b6fb1e58-5138-40b9-b796-adf0ed01500a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-76784ff5-c6ec-49ab-9b10-745438bb2493\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<d